@startuml
title Use Case A - Content Upsert Flow
skinparam shadowing false

start
:BusinessSystem\ncall POST /api/searchrec/index;
:SearchRecAPI\nparse body, validate\n**documents** non-empty list;
:SearchRecService.upsert_documents;
:IndexAdapter.upsert_documents;
note right
  **OpenSearch:** NDJSON bulk index
  **DbIndexAdapter (default when OpenSearch off):**
  transactional write to **doc** and **doc_term**
  (doc_key, lexical_norm_sq, …); delete old terms then insert
end note
:VectorAdapter.upsert_documents;
note right
  **Memory:** term sets from title/content/tags
  **Milvus / Qdrant:** HTTP upsert to remote collection
  **Qdrant:** local SimpleTextEmbeddingProvider\nencodes concatenated text → vector
end note
:FeatureStoreAdapter.upsert_documents;
note right
  **Memory:** doc_id → score_boost,\npopularity_score, freshness_score
  **Feast:** HTTP (when enabled)
end note
:Return API payload from\n**index adapter** result\n(e.g. upserted / total);
stop
@enduml
